<div style="float: left; width: 700px;">

<% end_time = Preference.competition_end_time
  if Time.now < end_time %>
These are the current results, competition isn't over yet though!  Remember the first purpose of the competition is to get feedback and learn how to be a better composer/author :)
<br/>
<br/>
<br/>
<% else %>
  <%= image_tag 'trophy.png' %>
<meta property="og:image" content="http://freeldssheetmusic.org/images/trophy.png" /> <!-- it worked -->

  <br/>
  We recently finished our yearly sheet music competition (for composers to get feedback) with some awesome entries. 
<br/>Competition this year is sponsored by <a href=https://www.amazon.com/As-Saints-Sing-Michael-Young/dp/1462140289/ref=sr_1_1?dchild=1&keywords=as+saints+we+sing&qid=1633404288&sr=8-1>As Saints We Sing</a>, a spiral bound collection of SATB music that includes 179 selections from dozens of Latter-day Saint lyricists and composers.
