<br/>
<% end %>
<hr/>
<br/>
<div style="width:50%; float:left;">
First the "open vote" category:
<br/>
<br/>
<% for p in @products %>
  <%= p.total_valid_competition_points %> points: <%= link_to(p.name, :controller=>'music', :action=>'show', :id => p.code) %> by <%= p.composer_tag.name %>
<div class="clear"></div>
<%= p.thumbnail_html_cache %>
<div class="clear"></div>
<% end %>

</div>

<div style="width:50%; float:left;">
And our peer review category winners (out of possible 5.0):
<br/>
<br/>
<% for p in @peer_review_products %>
  <%= "%.02f" % p.competition_peer_review_average %> : <%= link_to(p.name, :controller=>'music', :action=>'show', :id => p.code) %> by <%= p.composer_tag.name %>
  <div class="clear"></div>
<%= p.thumbnail_html_cache %>
<div class="clear"></div>
<% end %>
...

</div>
<div class="line clear"></div>

<div>
Want to learn more about the competition, check <%= link_to 'it out here', :controller => 'content_nodes', :action => 'show_by_name', :name => 'sheet-music-competition' %> for details.
</div>
<div>
Want to participate in the competition next year?  Create an <%= link_to 'account here', :controller => 'content_nodes', :action => 'show_by_name', :name => 'upload' %> and we'll email you a reminder about it!
